    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice for anyone who wants a dependable car that still looks and drives great. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a champ, and is totally ready for its next chapter with a new owner. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
