      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 981-generation mid-engine coupe featuring the 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six. This specimen is equipped with the 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission and the Sport Chrono package, providing lightning-fast actuation and optimized throttle mapping. The chassis features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) with adaptive damping for exceptional lateral stability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a PDK calibration and a full inspection of the direct fuel injection (DFI) system. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, maintaining excellent thermal dissipation. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering a visceral 7,400 RPM redline experience.",
